Create a Resume Builder web application similar to FlowCV using React (Next.js) and Firebase.

CORE FEATURES:
1. Landing page with hero section, features, templates preview, testimonials, FAQ
2. Firebase Authentication (Google + Email/Password)
3. Dashboard showing user's resumes with "Create New" option
4. Template selection page with 6+ professional templates
5. Resume editor with:
   - Content management (Personal info, Education, Experience, Skills, Projects)
   - Drag-and-drop section reordering
   - Real-time preview
   - Customization panel (colors, fonts, layout, spacing)
6. PDF export functionality
7. Auto-save to Firestore

TECH STACK:
- Next.js 14 (App Router)
- React 18
- Firebase (Auth, Firestore, Storage)
- Tailwind CSS
- Zustand (state management)
- Framer Motion (animations)
- html2canvas + jsPDF (PDF generation)
- react-beautiful-dnd (drag and drop)

DATABASE SCHEMA:
- users: { uid, email, displayName, photoURL, createdAt }
- resumes: { id, userId, name, templateId, content, customization, lastEdited }

IMPLEMENTATION PRIORITIES:
1. Setup Firebase project and authentication
2. Create landing page with auth modal
3. Build dashboard with resume list
4. Implement template system (start with 2-3 templates)
5. Create editor with split-screen layout
6. Add customization panel
7. Implement PDF export
8. Add auto-save functionality

Make it responsive, performant, and deployable on Vercel with minimal backend maintenance.


